 no suicide note, and said that if his brother chose to kill himself, he would not write a note.\n\nSource/custody note: this is a relevant-text extract from a public Business Insider article, not the full HTML page, not a court document, and not the original note image. It is submitted for authenticity and provenance weight, not as proof of the note image itself."}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1782800827874}]}
